         <div type="translation">
            <p>from the Eria (burial mound?) </p></div>
         
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>From the position of the 6th letter and through comparison with other inscriptions, the MFA website entry suggests "eirion/εἴριον" (burial mound), and cites IG I(3), Attica, no. 1395.</p>
